  <steps>
    <step order="1">Verify producer dual-write completed (task 021 status = ✅); query a sample `appnotification` row and confirm `sprk_category` populated</step>
    <step order="2">Open `notificationService.ts`; locate `$filter` composition path (built in task 040)</step>
    <step order="3">Add helper `buildDisabledChannelsFilter(disabled: string[])`: returns OData expression `sprk_category ne 'X' and sprk_category ne 'Y'` (no `not in` operator in OData v4 — use AND of `ne`)</step>
    <step order="4">Compose with existing `$filter` (timeWindow + dueWithinDays already in place); skip clause when disabled is empty</step>
    <step order="5">Read `disabledChannels` from preferences; default to `[]` if missing</step>
    <step order="6">Add Jest test: disabledChannels=['email']; assert `$filter` string contains `sprk_category ne 'email'`</step>
    <step order="7">Add Jest test: disabledChannels=[]; assert no `sprk_category` clause appears in query</step>
