  <notes>OData v4 has no `not in` — use AND of `ne`. Pre-requisite is task 021 (producer dual-write `sprk_category`). Owner Q&amp;A 2026-06-25 confirmed this column approach. R3 PR #451 file overlap — run conflict-check.</notes>
